OL,3,CThree charged after alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FFour ambulances from Hatzola were set
OL,7,Fon fire during the incident, as Aisha
OL,8,FZahid reports
OL,10,FThree people have been charged after
OL,11,Ffour Jewish community ambulances were
OL,12,Ftargeted in an alleged arson attack in
OL,13,Fnorth-west London.
OL,15,FHamza Iqbal, 20, and Rehan Khan, 19,
OL,16,Fboth British nationals from Leyton,
OL,17,Fand a 17-year-old boy, a dual British
OL,18,Fand Pakistani national from
OL,19,FWalthamstow, are due to appear at
OL,20,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,21,FSaturday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
