OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775499064
OL,3,CThree charged after alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FThey were charged with arson being
OL,7,Freckless as to whether life would be
OL,8,Fendangered after being arrested as
OL,9,Fpart of a Counter Terrorism Policing
OL,10,F(CTP) investigation.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
