FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775499064
OL,3,CThree charged after alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FFour ambulances from Hatzola, a
OL,7,Fvolunteer-led ambulance service
OL,8,Foperating in the Golders Green area of
OL,9,Fnorth-west London, were set on fire in
OL,10,Fthe early hours of March 23, causing
OL,11,Fgas canisters stored in the vehicles
OL,12,Fto explode.
OL,14,FCommander Helen Flanagan, head of
OL,15,FCounter Terrorism Policing London,
OL,16,Fsaid: "Since this appalling attack
OL,17,Flast week, we have been working
OL,18,Fcontinuously to investigate and
OL,19,Fidentify those responsible.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775499064
OL,3,CThree charged after alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,F"The investigation has now reached a
OL,7,Fstage where three people have been
OL,8,Fcharged and they will now appear in
OL,9,Fcourt."
OL,11,FTwo other men aged 45 and 47 who were
OL,12,Farrested last week, and are also
OL,13,FBritish, were released on bail until
OL,14,Flate April.
OL,16,FThe case is not being treated as
OL,17,Fterrorism but CTP said due to "the
OL,18,Fcircumstances of the incident" the
OL,19,Finvestigation is being led by its
OL,20,Fdetectives.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
