PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1775499064
OL,3,CThree charged after alleged arson
OL,4,Cattack on Jewish community ambulances
OL,6,FFrank Ferguson, head of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service's special crime
OL,8,Fand counter terrorism division said:
OL,9,F"We remind all concerned that criminal
OL,10,Fproceedings against these defendants
OL,11,Fare active and that they have the
OL,12,Fright to a fair trial.
OL,14,F"It is vital that there should be no
OL,15,Freporting, commentary or sharing of
OL,16,Finformation online which could in any
OL,17,Fway prejudice these proceedings."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
